.DT
is_discussion_position_valid
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
is_discussion_position_valid

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_discussion_position_valid -  This is a special function to be used with the discuss items to make sure that there is not another discussion item checking the same name.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_discussion_position_valid(string club_name,
string position)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^club_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the club to check
%^BOLD%^position%^RESET%^ - the position to check for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the position is being discussed as an item

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/inherit/club_discuss.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is a special function to be used with the discuss items to
make sure that there is not another discussion item checking the
same name.
.EP

